[It appears as though the dengue fever activity is now getting into full
swing in Central America with epidemic activity declared in Guatemala in
June, Honduras last week and now Costa Rica. None of the reports to date
have specified the serotypes prevalent in this year's activity. However,
the Costa Rican website states: "The serotypes in circulation since 1993
are DEN1 and DEN3." Limon is situated in the Region Huetar Atlantica - MPP
....................................jw/es
